<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bury-vt">bury <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'beri/    美 /'beri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>埋葬：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We needed to bury the dead bodies as quickly as possible to stop disease spreading.
我们需要尽快将尸体埋葬，以防止疾病扩散。</p><footer>译林⑥ – 4</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>埋藏；掩藏；遮盖：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The dog <strong>buried</strong> the bone <strong>in</strong> the ground. 
狗把骨头埋进了地里。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>buried</strong> his face <strong>in</strong> his hands. 
他双手掩面。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="be-buried-in-bury-oneself-in">be buried in / bury oneself in</h3>
<p>1.<strong>埋头于；专心致志于：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>As you know, I’m still buried in books at the school you are so familiar with. 
如你所知，我还在你所熟悉的那所学校埋头读书。</p></div></div>